  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join the Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/7ba3f8df38229eae7a8a2f9f9999bd42.poster.avif?t=1729119712\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/7ba3f8df38229eae7a8a2f9f9999bd42.webm?t=1729119712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/7ba3f8df38229eae7a8a2f9f9999bd42.mp4?t=1729119712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive the Night</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Survive until 6am in this immersive horror experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use the wall power switches to turn on the hallway lights which will deter any attacks from \"Whiskers\" but will use building power. Once you run out of building power you are helpless.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use the generator to charge your laptop which you can use to complete tasks to generate flashlight charges and manage your security system. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Listen closely and use flashlight charges to flash down different hallways to find where \"Whiskers\" is coming from.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/07fc342c902579a48a163aeb86804455.poster.avif?t=1729119712\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/07fc342c902579a48a163aeb86804455.webm?t=1729119712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/07fc342c902579a48a163aeb86804455.mp4?t=1729119712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Non-Linear Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Never have the same thing twice, through a strong AI built from the ground up for this game you will be able to play over and over again and still have fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Easter Eggs, you may experience something special when you play.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/7ba3f8df38229eae7a8a2f9f9999bd42.poster.avif?t=1729119712\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/7ba3f8df38229eae7a8a2f9f9999bd42.webm?t=1729119712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/7ba3f8df38229eae7a8a2f9f9999bd42.mp4?t=1729119712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive the Night</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Survive until 6am in this immersive horror experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use the wall power switches to turn on the hallway lights which will deter any attacks from \"Whiskers\" but will use building power. Once you run out of building power you are helpless.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use the generator to charge your laptop which you can use to complete tasks to generate flashlight charges and manage your security system. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Listen closely and use flashlight charges to flash down different hallways to find where \"Whiskers\" is coming from.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/07fc342c902579a48a163aeb86804455.poster.avif?t=1729119712\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/07fc342c902579a48a163aeb86804455.webm?t=1729119712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2706290/extras/07fc342c902579a48a163aeb86804455.mp4?t=1729119712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Non-Linear Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Never have the same thing twice, through a strong AI built from the ground up for this game you will be able to play over and over again and still have fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Easter Eggs, you may experience something special when you play.</p></li></ul>",
